OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with a
OL,6,Fmixture of late sunny spells and
OL,7,Fvariable cloud this evening. Remaining
OL,8,Fdry overnight with occasional clear
OL,9,Fspells. Winds easing and staying mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FGenerally cloudier on Sunday,
OL,12,Fwith cloud thick enough for the odd
OL,13,Fspot of rain, but largely dry. Feeling
OL,14,Fwarm in the sunny spells that develop.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,17,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Cloudier
OL,18,Ffrom Tuesday with a little rain at
OL,19,Ftimes towards the north. Turning
OL,20,Fwindier, especially by Wednesday.
OL,21,FRemaining rather warm throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
